name: You followed the instructions well, thank you.
description:
Special edition postage stamps for #itsmondayart by @mondayartclub.
This postage stamp was inspired by Radiohead's song Fitter Happier. Fitter Happier is a checklist of how to "better" yourself in the way society encourages, but these ways also subdue you and complicate your life to only concern yourself with this checklist. It's an endless cycle in a way. Ultimately, truth of self and life is lost in search of someone else's goals.
